Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/jsancio/dotfiles.git ~/.dotfiles

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/vim ~/.vim
    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/tmux.conf ~/.tmux.conf
    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/gitignore ~/.gitignore
    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/gitconfig ~/.gitconfig
    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/dircolors-solarized/dircolors.ansi-dark ~/.dircolors
    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/Xresources ~/.Xresources
    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/ctags ~/.ctags

    mkdir -p ~/.urxvt/ext
    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/urxvt/urxvt-perls/clipboard ~/.urxvt/ext/clipboard
    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/urxvt/urxvt-perls/keyboard-select ~/.urxvt/ext/keyboard-select

Switch to the `~/.dotfiles` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.dotfiles
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

To update the submodules:

    cd ~/.dotfiles
    git submodule foreach git pull
    git commit -am "Update to submodules"
